   └─ Copy docker-compose entry from SELF-IMPROVING-AGENTS-SETUP.md
   └─ Build image: docker build agents/goal_keeper/

Step 2: Update Each Agent to Report Metrics
   └─ Import MetricsEngine
   └─ Call record_task_completion() after each task
   └─ Include: duration, quality_score, cost, success/failure

Step 3: Register Agent Skills (Optional)
